fields.title: 2 girls 1 lemon pie
fields.plot: A girl eats a lemon pie and gets super powers. Under the name Lemon she vows  to make the world a better place ..until her nemesis Baking Soda appears. They battle for life, whitening and destroying teeth in the process. Baking soda though pulls out a dirty trick, reveals its disguise. It's been cocaine all along.. and it wants the world & everything in it. Lemon has a trick on her own. ELVIRA. Together they pie their nemesis off and celebrate a sweet victory. Lesbian scene included. Of course.

fields.title: The Killer Sea Doggos
fields.plot: A brave scientist bumps into a killer seal on his quest to explore Antarctica. The seal surprises the scientist by sneaking in front of him at 1m/h speed and attacks him ...violently...crushing his legs with his head. The brave scientist records everything on camera as he's trying to escape this monster. Eventually his fragile heart exploded of unethical cuteness. The press blames Obama. All seals were killed after the incident. By pollution. Which had nothing to do with the movie.  #ElonMusk

fields.title: I am a fish
fields.content: Fish are great sea creatures that don't have legs or hands. They are legless and handless. That is why they never evolved to mermaids. Our goal is to put enough pollution into the ocean so the fish mutate. They will develop several hands and legs, maybe even few human heads. Over time, we will have mermaids, and mermen, and the world will be great.
